summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of a portion of the east 40.25 feet of Tract J and a portion of Tract I, Alki Point Addition, together with Second Class Tide Lands adjoining and portion of Block 467, Seattle Tide Lands Extension No. 1 adjoining, with respect to Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 17-148.
